              "fill": "$text-primary",
              "textGrowth": "fixed-width",
              "width": "fill_container",
              "content": "Meeting Notes - March 25, 2026\n\nAttendees: Sarah, Jake, Maria, Tom\n\nAgenda:\n1. Q1 review\n2. Product roadmap update\n3. Hiring plan\n\n---\n\nQ1 Review\n- Revenue up 12% from last quarter\n- Active users crossed 50k milestone\n- Churn reduced to 3.2%\n- Support tickets down 18%\n\nProduct Roadmap\n- v2.1 shipping next week (dark mode, export)\n- v2.2 planned for May (collaboration, sharing)\n- Mobile app kicked off, targeting July beta\n- API v3 in research phase\n\nHiring\n- 2 senior engineers (backend)\n- 1 designer (product)\n- Interviews starting next week\n\nAction Items:\n[ ] Sarah: send Q1 deck to board by Friday\n[ ] Jake: finalize v2.1 release notes\n[ ] Maria: post designer job listing\n[ ] Tom: schedule backend interviews\n\nNext meeting: April 1, 2026 at 10am",
              "lineHeight": 1.8,
              "fontFamily": "JetBrains Mono",
              "fontSize": 14,
              "fontWeight": "normal"
            }
          ]
        },
